cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "SCN-LLM Prototype: a synthetic reference implementation of the SCN temporal module"
abstract: >-
  A single-machine synthetic reference implementation of an SCN-inspired temporal
  module for large language models: a coupled Van der Pol oscillator clock,
  phase-response entrainment to a synthetic zeitgeber, an analytic 16-D
  temporal-state map, and a toy phase-modulated retrieval path, with a reproducible
  four-figure mechanism-and-cost evaluation.
type: software
authors:
